Members of the Regional Board of Education shall be elected in the same manner as other Town officers. Said members shall serve four (4) year terms. The Town shall elect members of the Regional District #8 Board of Education in the manner provided for by Sections [[10-46 (a) and (c)|https://www.cga.ct.gov/current/pub/chap_164.htm#sec_10-46]] of the General Statutes as amended from time to time.